data.title: Isomerization of Epoxides into Allylic Alcohols Catalyzed by Supported Au Nanoparticles on TiO2: A Mechanistic Insight
data.meta_description: Based on primary and β-secondary isotope effects, it is established that the isomerization of epoxides into allylic alcohols catalyzed by supported Au nanoparticles proceeds via an unsymmetrical concerted transition state in which there is partial positive charge developing on the C-O carbon atom pr …
